Coal are categorised and/or to be categorised in terms and in accordance 
with the relevant notifications issued by the Seller and/or the Government of 
India and published in the public domain and/or the Gazette of India, as 
applicable. The basis of grading for different categories of Coal are as 
under: 

(i) 
non-coking Coal: based on GCV bands; 
(ii) 
coking Coal: based on ash percentage; and 
(iii) semi-coking Coal: based on (ash + moisture) percentage; 

